service: analytics-dashboard-api

provider:
  name: aws
  runtime: nodejs20.x
  region: us-east-1
  stage: dev
  environment:
    DB_HOST: ${env:DB_HOST}
    DB_USER: ${env:DB_USER}
    DB_PASS: ${env:DB_PASS}
    DB_NAME: ${env:DB_NAME}
    DB_PORT: ${env:DB_PORT}
  iamRoleStatements:
    - Effect: Allow
      Action:
        - ec2:CreateNetworkInterface
        - ec2:DescribeNetworkInterfaces
        - ec2:DeleteNetworkInterface
        - ec2:AssignPrivateIpAddresses
        - ec2:UnassignPrivateIpAddresses
      Resource: "*"
  vpc:
    securityGroupIds:
      - sg-07f8e5e39b6c2c687
    subnetIds:
      - subnet-002067f89a3e5fad2
      - subnet-06f348836099aef56

functions:
  health:
    handler: handler.health
    events:
      - http:
          path: /api/health
          method: get
          cors:
            origin: '*'
            headers:
              - Content-Type
              - X-Amz-Date
              - Authorization
              - X-Api-Key
              - X-Amz-Security-Token
              - x-user-id
              - X-User-Id
            allowCredentials: true
  
  setup:
    handler: setup.handler
    events:
      - http:
          path: /api/setup
          method: get
          cors: true
  
  migrate:
    handler: migrate.handler
    events:
      - http:
          path: /api/migrate
          method: get
          cors: true
  
  getEntries:
    handler: handler.getEntries
    events:
      - http:
          path: /api/entries
          method: get
          cors:
            origin: '*'
            headers:
              - Content-Type
              - X-Amz-Date
              - Authorization
              - X-Api-Key
              - X-Amz-Security-Token
              - x-user-id
              - X-User-Id
            allowCredentials: true
  
  createEntry:
    handler: handler.createEntry
    events:
      - http:
          path: /api/entries
          method: post
          cors:
            origin: '*'
            headers:
              - Content-Type
              - X-Amz-Date
              - Authorization
              - X-Api-Key
              - X-Amz-Security-Token
              - x-user-id
              - X-User-Id
            allowCredentials: true
